CWEAVE is based on WEAVE, so search places where xord is used in WEAVE and use it in CWEAVE
in analogous place; then use changes which were removed in commit c775b2147d53ea3f0183368cf261f4940955a619 of utf8/build.sh

CP1251 locale cannot be used (C.UTF-8 must be used) - islower and isupper will not work, so use iswlower(xchr[c]) and iswupper(xchr[c]) instead
